snes9express
------------------------------------------
Snes9express is a graphical interface for the X11 versions of snes9x,
featuring an organized layout of common snes9x options.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.36.11-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.88.1-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.24.33-1
  libpango1.0_0-1.57.1-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0-devel-2.36.11-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.88.1-1
  libgtk2.0-devel-2.24.33-1
  libpango1.0-devel-1.57.1-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://snes9express.app/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/snes9express/snes9express-1.43.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack snes9express-1.43-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./snes9express-1.43-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/snes9express-1.43-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/snes9express-1.43-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(snes9express)
  /usr/bin/snes9express.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/snes9express.README
  /usr/share/doc/snes9express/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/snes9express/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/snes9express/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/snes9express/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/snes9express/README
  /usr/share/snes9express/snes.s9xskin
  /usr/share/snes9express/snsp.s9xskin

